reviewText: I bought this DVD from Marvelio and it was a bootleg DVD! Meaning it was an illegal copy and it would not play!
It was decent for what it was. Nothing spectacular but don't regret buying it. Especially when it's a DVD that is not too easy to obtain. Good for a few jumps.

I have read the book based on the Skinwalker Ranch and this movie brings it to life. The movie follows the events at the ranch in a liberal manner. I was hoping for a more closely depiction of the actual events but this movie captures the frightening phenomenon that continues to this day. I would recommend watching this movie even if you are familiar with the unearthly encounters so familiar with the area.
